The author praises Tom Carper, who they have known for nearly 50 years, as a dedicated and trusted colleague. They highlight his commitment to serving the people of Delaware and his ability to work across party lines to achieve results. Carper's leadership has had a significant impact on the state, including strengthening the economy, protecting the environment, and improving infrastructure. As a member of the Senate Finance Committee and Chairman of the Senate Committee on Environment and Public Works, Carper played a key role in passing the Affordable Care Act and addressing climate change. His advocacy for veterans' healthcare is also recognized. Additionally, Carper has inspired young Delawareans to pursue careers in public service. The author expresses gratitude for Carper's leadership and looks forward to continuing to work with him in the future.